KCCAns: Spray copper oxycloride @ 2 gram in 1 litre of water
spray dimethoate @ 1 ml / lt of water
spary imidachloprid 1 ml /3 litre of water
Good variety of maize- saktiman 1-4, ganga-11, suan, devki
spray plantomycin 1 ml/12 ltr+mencozeb 2g/ ltr. of water
Leaf spot can be controlled by spraying Zineb or Mancozeb 2 g/lit.
